        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Svätý Jur - Neštich 3D"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hradisko <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/2010/09/hradisko-nestych.html\">Nešich v Svätom Jure</a> patrí medzi najvýznamnejšie a najmohutnejšie slovanské hradiská na Slovensku. Náš spolupracovník Jakub Španiel (  <a data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.jakubspaniel.eu&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1625029963221000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGk4rgB4qgsvIWnzI09Ha_0MjV3kQ\" href=\"http://www.jakubspaniel.eu\" target=\"_blank\">www.jakubspaniel.eu</a> ) vytvoril veľmi pôsobivú vizualizáciu&nbsp; možného vzhľadu hradiska&nbsp; na konci 9. storočia. Za podklay k 3D LIDARu, čo je neoceniteľná pomoc, ďakujeme Tiborovi Lieskovskému.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjlr6e8C3wdwSMO-mIc1xVK2Y3EYBc7JX-1yPAPHGMHTBaNtwxlRP181-4-b5eiJR23F_DUaVI2eK-vi1TexoY7CMQAD6L0Li0UcHHTv9Y6ZQiAQ5ZIC2z9X1mME147mBOlnyhST6v-Eizl/s2048/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+Sever+JS_male.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1084\" data-original-width=\"2048\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjlr6e8C3wdwSMO-mIc1xVK2Y3EYBc7JX-1yPAPHGMHTBaNtwxlRP181-4-b5eiJR23F_DUaVI2eK-vi1TexoY7CMQAD6L0Li0UcHHTv9Y6ZQiAQ5ZIC2z9X1mME147mBOlnyhST6v-Eizl/s320/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+Sever+JS_male.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgaPiKGtJU0hJC3Ow14UFNsOrj87ZdatBDwQWzIxzfs_qBrtAST_GG6WzcfkGwJXHtp4Q8aSX6PFyjZYIwZZBKo89788KBG_XBUNvNZzBRyx4JyjgC0n3B0mmjGvYcjX3-V3oQM1Y3Mqg_P/s2048/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+Juh+JS_male.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1084\" data-original-width=\"2048\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgaPiKGtJU0hJC3Ow14UFNsOrj87ZdatBDwQWzIxzfs_qBrtAST_GG6WzcfkGwJXHtp4Q8aSX6PFyjZYIwZZBKo89788KBG_XBUNvNZzBRyx4JyjgC0n3B0mmjGvYcjX3-V3oQM1Y3Mqg_P/s320/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+Juh+JS_male.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6ittpkXeH5b8O5h8__Ck5YeUCQTbt4KMA-BAFmN3kbUpSDNua9jzbed0Z3HfiD35AMqqJUqo7AGd3PxQnSpRLohqY1dNOCVCmE0xIvAjWxGlPKRNJm5l_DBnbFPwbE9kFaMyp2PsWiXO-/s2048/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+cele+JS_male.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1084\" data-original-width=\"2048\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6ittpkXeH5b8O5h8__Ck5YeUCQTbt4KMA-BAFmN3kbUpSDNua9jzbed0Z3HfiD35AMqqJUqo7AGd3PxQnSpRLohqY1dNOCVCmE0xIvAjWxGlPKRNJm5l_DBnbFPwbE9kFaMyp2PsWiXO-/s320/Nes%25CC%258Ctich+cele+JS_male.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"BLOG_video_class\" height=\"266\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G3XV7sUC2MQ\" width=\"320\" youtube-src-id=\"G3XV7sUC2MQ\"></iframe></div><br /><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></p>"
